42db727e1907ec295038394e44d38334e0593623561c56fc1946493cfb24af4987f5aa16f2d1fd2510a7b7155f7d7d4cdc14cae449ea074414874ac28e380fb4  0001-quirks-Pine64-PineBook-Pro-keyboard.patch
"
